snippet.title: Live In Your Reality
snippet.description:
Visualize your personal collections into an immersive world where your media is showcased as never before.

Your mind holds an endless world of media waiting to be unleashed.  With AArcade as your tool, you have the power to forge this living world around you.  A world that grows along side you over the months & years that you spend there.

Since 2010 AArcade has been visualizing the real metaverse with the time-tested formula of a generic shortcut launcher, very much like Windows itself.

Shortcuts are not going out of style, and AArcade's newest version adds a slick UI and performance optimizations to make it prettier & more functional than ever before.
